  / Steps section
  %section#works.section-steps
    .row
      %h2 How it works – Simple as 1, 2, 3
      .row
        .col-md-3
        .col-md-6
          .works-step
            %div 1
            %p Choose the subscription plan that best fits your needs and sign up today.
          .works-step
            %div 2
            %p Order your delicious meal using our mobile app or website. Or you can even call us!
          .works-step
            %div 3
            %p Enjoy your meal after less than 20 minutes. See you the next time!

  / Cities section
  %section#cities.section-cities
    .row
      .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
        .service-box
          %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-cutlery.wow.bounceIn.text-primary
          %h2 Personalized Meals
          %h3.text-muted Meals catered to your liking.
      .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
        .service-box
          %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-globe.wow.bounceIn.text-primary
          %h2 Vast Selection
          %h3.text-muted Choose from cuisines from all over the world.
      .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
        .service-box
          %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-clock-o.wow.bounceIn.text-primary
          %h2 Reliable Service
          %h3.text-muted We deliver daily and within 1 hour of your order.
      .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
        .service-box
          %i.fa.fa-4x.fa-heart.wow.bounceIn.text-primary
          %h2 Dietary Labelling
          %h3.text-muted We have gluten-free, kosher, halal, vegan and much more.

  / Testimonials section
  %section.section-testimonials
    .row
      %h2 Are you a caterer?
    .row
      .col-md-4
        %blockquote
          Online Catering is just awesome! I just launched a startup which leaves me with no time for cooking, so Online Catering is a life-saver. Now that I got used to it, I couldn't live without my daily meals!
          %cite
            %img{:alt => "First customer", :src => "/images/customer-1.jpg"}/
            Alberto Duncan
      .col-md-4
        %blockquote
          Inexpensive, healthy and great-tasting meals, delivered right to my home. We have lots of food delivery here in Lisbon, but no one comes even close to Omifood. Me and my family are so in love!
          %cite
            %img{:alt => "Second customer", :src => "/images/customer-2.jpg"}/
            Joana Silva
      .col-md-4
        %blockquote
          I was looking for a quick and easy food delivery service in San Franciso. I tried a lot of them and ended up with Online Catering. Best food delivery service in the Bay Area. Keep up the great work!
          %cite
            %img{:alt => "Third customer", :src => "/images/customer-3.jpg"}/
            Milton Chapman
    .row.text-center.caterer-section
      %button.btn.btn-success.caterer Become a Caterer

  .row.last
    .col-md-3
    .col-md-6
      %h1.text-center Keep in touch!
      %form.contact-form{:action => "#", :method => "post"}
        .row
          .col.span-1-of-3
            %label{:for => "name"} Name
          .col.span-2-of-3
            %input#name{:name => "name", :placeholder => "Your name", :required => "", :type => "text"}/
        .row
          .col.span-1-of-3
            %label{:for => "email"} Email
          .col.span-2-of-3
            %input#email{:name => "email", :placeholder => "Your email", :required => "", :type => "email"}/
        .row
          .col.span-1-of-3
            %label{:for => "find-us"} How did you find us?
          .col.span-2-of-3
            %select#find-us{:name => "find-us"}
              %option{:selected => "selected", :value => "friends"} Friends
              %option{:value => "search"} Search engine
              %option{:value => "ad"} Advertisement
              %option{:value => "other"} Other
        .row
          .col.span-1-of-3
            %label Newsletter
          .col.span-2-of-3
            %input#news{:checked => "checked", :name => "news", :type => "checkbox"}/
            Yes, please
        .row
          .col.span-1-of-3
            %label Drop us a line
          .col.span-2-of-3
            %textarea{:name => "message", :placeholder => "Your message"}
        .row
          .col.span-1-of-3
            %label  
          .col.span-2-of-3
            %input{:type => "submit", :value => "Send it!"}/

